    public class Escape
extends jbt.execution.task.leaf.action.ExecutionAction
    ExecutionAction class created from MMPM action Escape. Implements the behaviour of the ghost escaping Pacman. Note : entering this behaviour assumes the position of Pacman is known This is checked by the IsPacManInSight condition
